        </item>
        <item>
            <title>SpaceX 公开飞船工厂 Starfactory　目标每年生产千艘 Starship 上火星</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/psacex-starfactory/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=psacex-starfactory</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/psacex-starfactory/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 07:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SpaceX]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Starship]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1268916</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前往我们报道过，Elon Musk 旗下航天制造商和太空运输公司 SpaceX 10 月 13 日于美国德州成功发射 Starship（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/spacex-starship-5th-launch/fun-tech/">相关报道</a>）。针对 Starship 试飞活动，SpaceX 在发射前夕于 X （前称 Twitter）发布了一条约 2 分钟长的影片，介绍其位于美国德州占地 100 万平方呎的 Starfactory。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-media-max-width="560"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">The 1-million square foot Starfactory brings many parts of the manufacturing process under one roof for the first time, moving as much system integration work as possible earlier in the build process, with the goal of eventually producing 1,000 Ships a year <a href="https://t.co/vz44XcTTN8">pic.twitter.com/vz44XcTTN8</a></p><p>— SpaceX (@SpaceX) <a href="https://twitter.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 13, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>SpaceX 位于美国德州博卡奇卡（Boca Chica）的 Starfactory 规模庞大，占地 100 万平方呎，有效整合飞船制造工序，在同一地点集中多个生产过程，可提前进行系统集成工作。据 SpaceX 帖文表示，Starfactory 目标是年产 1,000 艘飞船。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130730-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130730-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130730.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130712-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130712-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130712.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130657-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130657-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130657.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130644-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130644-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130644.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130816-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130816-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130816.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130750-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130750-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241014130750.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><p>「Starship」是 SpaceX 项目中的重要环节，目标是让人类实现星际旅行，并且其大规模的生产需要一个高效的制造体系来支援。Elon Musk 曾经表示，Starfactory 仅属起点，展望未来盼能年产 1,000 艘 Starship，作为迈向火星的基础。据媒体报道，目前 Starfactory 年产 100 枚火箭，即平均每 3 日可生产一枚火箭。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1007/1007919.htm">快科技</a>、<a href="https://x.com/SpaceX/status/1845434891430920423">SpaceX@X</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/spacex-starship-5th-launch/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SpaceX「筷子」机械臂回收火箭，睇片极似磁吸一样夹住</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/18/elon-musk-says-spacex-will-sue-faa-for-regulatory-overreach/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SpaceX 将提告美国联邦航空总署　Elon Musk 指其过度监管</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/27/louis-vuitton-spacex-rocket-may-happen/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">LVMH 总裁与 Elon Mask 会面　曾商讨 SpaceX 与 LV 合作</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/psacex-starfactory/fun-tech/">SpaceX 公开飞船工厂 Starfactory　目标每年生产千艘 Starship 上火星</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/psacex-starfactory/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
